Package foundation.omni.json.pojo

Class OmniPropertyInfo

  • java.lang.Object
    • foundation.omni.rpc.SmartPropertyListInfo
      • foundation.omni.json.pojo.OmniPropertyInfo
  • public class OmniPropertyInfo
extends SmartPropertyListInfo
    JSON bean representing the set of information on an Omni Property as returned by the omni_getproperty RPC method. It is a subclass of SmartPropertyListInfo because it is a superset of that information.

      OmniPropertyInfo​(SmartPropertyListInfo sptListInfo)
      Construct OmniPropertyInfo from SmartPropertyListInfo Since there is no way to fetch OmniPropertyInfo for all properties with a single request, this converter can be used to create a OmniPropertyInfo from a SmartPropertyListInfo with default values for the extra fields.
